'''苯并咪唑'''是一个多环[[芳香化合物|芳香]][[杂环化合物|杂环化合物]]，由[[苯|苯]]和[[咪唑|咪唑]]并合而成，分子式为C<sub>7</sub>H<sub>6</sub>N<sub>2</sub>。[[维生素B12|维生素B12]]分子中，5,6-二甲基苯并咪唑为[[碱基|碱基]]与[[钴|钴]]中心相连。<ref>{{cite journal
| author = H. A. Barker, R. D. Smyth, H. Weissbach, J. I. Toohey, J. N. Ladd, and B. E. Volcani
| title = Isolation and Properties of Crystalline Cobamide Coenzymes Containing Benzimidazole or 5,6-Dimethylbenzimidazole
| journal = [[Journal_of_Biological_Chemistry|Journal of Biological Chemistry]]
| year = 1960
| volume = 235
| issue = 2
| pages = 480–488
| url = http://www.jbc.org/cgi/reprint/235/2/480
| access-date = 2008-07-02
| archive-date = 2009-02-11
| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20090211194301/http://www.jbc.org/cgi/reprint/235/2/480
| dead-url = no
}}</ref>

苯并咪唑与[[咪唑|咪唑]]类似，也是制备[[氮杂环卡宾|氮杂环卡宾]]的常用原料。此类卡宾由N,N'-二取代的苯并咪唑用碱在2-位[[去质子化|去质子化]]制得，用于制取[[过渡金属卡宾配合物|过渡金属卡宾配合物]]。<ref>{{cite journal | author = R. Jackstell, A. Frisch, M. Beller, D. Rottger, M. Malaun and B. Bildstein | title = Efficient telomerization of 1,3-butadiene with alcohols in the presence of in situ generated palladium(0)carbene complexes | year = 2002 | journal = [[Journal_of_Molecular_Catalysis_A:_Chemical|Journal of Molecular Catalysis A: Chemical]] | volume = 185 | issue = 1-2 | pages = 105–112 | doi = 10.1016/S1381-1169(02)00068-7}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal | author = H. V. Huynh, J. H. H. Ho, T. C. Neo and L. L. Koh | title = Solvent-controlled selective synthesis of a trans-configured benzimidazoline-2-ylidene palladium(II) complex and investigations of its Heck-type catalytic activity | year = 2005 | journal = [[Journal_of_Organometallic_Chemistry|Journal of Organometallic Chemistry]] | volume = 690 | issue = 16 | pages = 3854–3860 | doi = 10.1016/j.jorganchem.2005.04.053}}</ref>

== 制备 ==

苯并咪唑由[[邻苯二胺|邻苯二胺]]与[[甲酸|甲酸]]<ref name = wagner>{{OrgSynth | title = Benzimidazole | prep = cv2p0065 | collvol = 2 | collvolpages = 65 | year = 1943 | author = E. C. Wagner and W. H. Millett}}</ref> 或等量[[原甲酸|原甲酸]]三甲酯缩合制得：

: C<sub>6</sub>H<sub>4</sub>(NH<sub>2</sub>)<sub>2</sub>  +  HC(OCH<sub>3</sub>)<sub>3</sub>  →  C<sub>6</sub>H<sub>4</sub>N(NH)CH  +  3 [[甲醇|CH<sub>3</sub>OH]]

2-取代的苯并咪唑可由此法用其他羧酸制备。<ref name = wagner/>

